 &lt;h2 id=&#34;The-Grand-Roster&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#The-Grand-Roster&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;The Grand Roster&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;The Grand Roster&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The majority of entries (800+) are provided by &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:K1NKR@arrl.net&#34;&gt;James W. “Skip” Youngberg K1NKR&lt;/a&gt; through his decades of research. Also, &lt;a href=&#34;sstuart5@cox.net&#34;&gt;Steve Stuart N6IA&lt;/a&gt; informed hundreds of entries dated back to 1970-74.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We rely on crowd-sourcing to make information accurate and updated. To nominate a W2SZ-affiliated individual, fill out &lt;a href=&#34;https://forms.gle/drVtrJS7ywm9Vowy5&#34;&gt;this form&lt;/a&gt;. If you identify inaccuracies or own W2SZ archives, please &lt;a href=&#34;/contact&#34;&gt;email an officer&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
